{"tid":2298494,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：追究警黑勾結 林卓廷開Patreon以戰養戰（李八方）","createTime":"2020-11-24T05:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T05:47:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"03381b5db19afd3f4fe38651f74939b04c9ce408","tid":2298494,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:47:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/NR4ORHGCVJF3VH2PO3EGZZ65QY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2FNR4ORHGCVJF3VH2PO3EGZZ65QY%2F&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=67446b2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201124%2FNR4ORHGCVJF3VH2PO3EGZZ65QY%2F&h=a0b46ed7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201124/NR4ORHGCVJF3VH2PO3EGZZ65QY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：追究警黑勾結 林卓廷開Patreon以戰養戰（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2tMWqgi6JVXiLigg8qxpiyY3z-c=/785x466/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PNLZTSUUKNDKJPLLFQFYATMWXE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2tMWqgi6JVXiLigg8qxpiyY3z-c%3D%2F785x466%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPNLZTSUUKNDKJPLLFQFYATMWXE.jpg&h=b134a93a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林卓廷（圓圖）製作了登記Patreon懶人包予支持者參考。<br />\n<br />\n辭任議會對民主派而言，係一章終結，亦係新章開端，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n八方問過阿廷，佢話開Patreon都係以戰養戰，事關未來要繼續加強香港同海外論述、延續新東地區工作，唔係佢一人之力可承擔，要靠同佢並肩作戰多年嘅好同事，分工合作。所以佢好希望盡量留住呢班年輕、有理想、肯承擔、敢於抗爭嘅好手足，維持團隊成員，以便長期抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藉平台針砭時弊<br />\n<br />\n佢個人都孭緊七單刑事同民事官司，雖然部份有基金支持，但訟費壓力都好沉重，佢亦需要同事協助搜集同整理證據，呢啲一切都要資源。當然佢亦想keep住有個平台，同大家針砭時弊，唔畀政府隨意改寫歷史。佢希望大家可以登記成為佢Patreon用戶，集腋成裘，中大畢業嘅佢表明自必「無負重託，艱險奮進」。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷的Patreon網頁係：<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/cheuktinglam，關心同支持佢嘅市民可以去睇睇。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fcheuktinglam%EF%BC%8C%E9%97%9C%E5%BF%83%E5%90%8C%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%BD%A2%E5%98%85%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E5%8E%BB%E7%9D%87%E7%9D%87%E3%80%82&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=1c583c6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/cheuktinglam，關心同支持佢嘅市民可以去睇睇。</a><br />\n<br />\n李八方"}]}